    "Html": "Here is the detailed solution for people of same WPF level as myself :) <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNB: the solution for non-autogeneratecolumns; the solution is the <strong>same fast</strong> as if without colouring (!)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Add namespace to the Window element (very first element in XAML)<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nxmlns</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">my</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;http://schemas.microsoft.com/wpf/2008/toolkit&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>2. Add cell style with style triggers in your resources (e.g. your Window resources):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Window.Resources</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\">Key</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;<strong>DataGridCellStyle</strong>&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> TargetType</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> my</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\">DataGridCell</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">}&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Style.Triggers</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataTrigger</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> IsPriceUp</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">}&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">                &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Property</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Foreground&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Green&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">            &lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataTrigger</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataTrigger</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> IsPriceUp</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">}&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;false&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">                &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Property</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Foreground&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Red&quot; /&gt;            <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">            &lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataTrigger</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Style.Triggers</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Style</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">. . .<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n3. Bind the column cell style<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">my</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> . . .</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> AutoGenerateColumns</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;False&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">my</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataGrid.Columns</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">&gt; . . .<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">my</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=Price}&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> Header</span><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Price&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> <br>\r\n<strong>                        CellStyle</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">StaticResource</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000\"> DataGridCellStyle</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><strong>}&quot; </strong>/&gt; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>4. Implement change notifications in C#.. eg:<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"><br>\r\n    IsPriceUp = newPrice &gt; </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">this</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.Price;<br>\r\n    </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">this</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.Price = newPrice;<br>\r\n    NotifyPropertyChanged(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;Price&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">);<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">    NotifyPropertyChanged(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">&quot;IsPriceUp&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">);\r\n<p><strong>Enjoy ! :)</strong></p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
